nark dragons have not been up more than maby an hour or two before being killed. Mostly by wizards Manaburning. I know for a fact, that a few wizards have been doing this to get phat lewtz and mad cash. Now, what is my beef with this.<br><br>First of all, this is a GIMP way of getting cash. Secondly, by doing so, you are taking away content from the corresponding tier guilds, who might have wanted to kill the mobs in the regular way.<br><br>A few wizards might argue that they are doing this to help a friend or guildy get their epic piece because their raid wiped with 50 people or so. Now, in theory, this would be ok once or twice. BUT, in reality what is happening, is no different from what velks is doing. Encounters are being gimped, and people are taking the easy way out to get their shit. What this produces in the long run is poorly skilled highlevel players wanting to join the &quot;highend&quot; game.<br><br>Having just gotten their epic, applying to &lt;insert uberguild here&gt; to get more phat lewtz or raid shit is just natural, right ? Well, not only are these people lacking basic raid experience, but they have been participating in removing content from other players to learn of.<br><br>As said earlier, a few wizards on this server have been burning mobs for phat lewtz to sell, without thinking about the corresponding tier guilds loosing out on content to play. Now, the excuses some have given me is, kunark is so easy, it doesnt matter. Well, if it is so damn easy, go make a REGULAR GROUP and try killing &lt;insert mob here&gt; with less people in the regular way, actually earning the kill. It takes no skill to MB, at all.<br><br>Also, with the rising interrest for instakilling mobs with MB, on the wizards forums on lanys, the idea to start Manaburning Sontalak has arisen. Question is, where will this end. Sontalak is a mob with 90k hps, so MBing him is pretty simple. Klandicar has about 80k hps, Zlandicar has around 90k. More content to instakil